<section id="lineage" class="lineage-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">From Fire to the Abyss</h2>

    <div class="lineage-narrative">
      <p>
        Abject grew from the ashes of <a href="https://firestr.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="fire-link">Fire★</a>, a peer-to-peer
        platform for creating and sharing distributed applications. Fire★ called it
        <strong>Grass Computing</strong>: software you can touch, shape, and share directly.
        No cloud. No landlords.
      </p>
      <p>
        Fire★ proved the vision: encrypted P2P communication, live collaborative coding,
        apps that spread through conversations. But it dreamed in C++ and Lua.
      </p>
      <p>
        Abject is the next incarnation. The same soul in a new body: TypeScript and WASM,
        Canvas compositing, and an LLM that negotiates between incompatible minds.
        The grass still grows. Now it thinks.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="evolution">
      <div class="evo-card evo-fire">
        <h3>Fire★</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>C++ / Qt / Lua</li>
          <li>RSA 4096 encryption</li>
          <li>Manual app sharing</li>
          <li>firelocator for peer discovery</li>
          <li><a href="https://firestr.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="evo-link">firestr.com</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="evo-arrow">
        <span class="arrow-glyph">→</span>
      </div>

      <div class="evo-card evo-abjects">
        <h3>Abject</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>TypeScript / WASM / Canvas</li>
          <li>ECDSA/ECDH + AES-256-GCM</li>
          <li>LLM-mediated protocol negotiation</li>
          <li>Signaling server for peer discovery</li>
          <li><span class="evo-link">abject.world</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .lineage-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-deep) 0%, #0a0810 50%, var(--bg-deep) 100%);
  }

  .lineage-narrative {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .lineage-narrative p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .lineage-narrative .fire {
    color: #ff9f43;
  }

  .lineage-narrative strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .evolution {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .evo-card {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .evo-fire {
    border-color: rgba(255, 159, 67, 0.2);
  }

  .evo-fire:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 159, 67, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 159, 67, 0.08);
  }

  .evo-fire h3 {
    color: #ff9f43;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .evo-abjects {
    border-color: var(--border-accent);
  }

  .evo-abjects:hover {
    border-color: rgba(57, 255, 142, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--eldritch-glow);
  }

  .evo-abjects h3 {
    color: var(--eldritch);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .evo-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .evo-card li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .fire-link {
    color: #ff9f43;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 159, 67, 0.3);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .fire-link:hover {
    border-color: #ff9f43;
  }

  .evo-link {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 112, 0.3);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .evo-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  .evo-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .arrow-glyph {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--void-purple);
    text-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--void-purple-glow);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .evolution {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .evo-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
  }
</style>
